{
  "stem": "8610.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But we were glad to see the back of this, this-- of this, this death camp, as we called it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As I said, they brought in flamethrowers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There's only one way, and that was to burn it to the ground, in the hope they will destroy the lice at the same time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Little did I realize that the lice were coming out of the ground after the place had been burned.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was a hell camp when it was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was a hell camp when it was finished.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wasn't there at the time that they-- but I heard that the-- the army brought in the flamethrowers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they just burned the huts to the ground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were wooden huts, after all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was easy enough to burn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then came the question of, what are we going to do with the survivors?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no guarantee that all those who were brought into the-- into the hospital would survive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had deaths there, too, but not as many.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I must say that the medical services were fantastic then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had two or three British general hospitals were transferred.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had nurses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had doctors, all under the command of the chief medical officer of Second Army, a man by the name of Brigadier Glyn Hughes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I must mention his name because to me, he was man of Belsen.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
